window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>- From Kindle Storyteller Award Winner, G J Ogden -</i></b></p> <p><b>A spark of rebellion can topple an empire.</b></p> <p>When Finn Brasa is thrust into a deadly gladiatorial battle against high-tech assassins and intelligent robots, it's all for the entertainment of the masses.<br> <br> No one expected him to survive - least of all, Finn himself.<br> <br> His reward? Status and riches. But what Finn truly hungers for is revolution. The common people are desperate for a leader to rise up and challenge the ruthless empire that has subjugated humanity for centuries.<br> <br> From the streets of Earth’s last city to the colossal space station Nimbus, Finn will stop at nothing to crush humanity’s high-tech overlords.<br> <br> He’s beaten the odds before - but can one man really bring down an empire?<br> <br> <b>Fans of sci-fi adventure, daring rebellions, and epic battles against deadly AI will love Metal and Blood. Listen to the complete series in this thrilling box set.</b></p>"; 
